        <div class="comment">
            <h3>
                <span class="comment-vote">
                    <span id="c-1006638909" class="vote-count">1</span>
                        <a href="javascript:;" id="btn-1006638909" class="j a_show_login" data-cid="1006638909">有用</a>
                </span>
                <span class="comment-info">
                    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/shijianchangsha/">四廢書房主人</a>
                        <span class="user-stars allstar30 rating" title="还行"></span>
                    <span>2016-02-01</span>
                </span>
            </h3>
            <p class="comment-content">优点是便于获得，排版也算友好。但校勘实在是硬伤，且删去武内义雄的校记，等于是把最有价值的部分给扔了，完全搞不懂。</p>
        </div>
    </li>

                
    <li class="comment-item" data-cid="797090983">
        <div class="comment">
